our nervous systems

00:02:37.990 --> 00:02:39.460 align:middle line:90%
get recalibrated.

00:02:39.460 --> 00:02:41.680 align:middle line:84%
During the process
of recalibration,

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:44.740 align:middle line:84%
the nervous system is what
triggers the fight or flight--

00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:46.960 align:middle line:90%
is what causes us to take sides.

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:49.090 align:middle line:84%
So in effect, we
have an entire world

00:02:49.090 --> 00:02:53.230 align:middle line:84%
going through a massive
healing and awakening process,

00:02:53.230 --> 00:02:56.740 align:middle line:84%
not knowing the inner workings
of the healing process.

00:02:56.740 --> 00:03:00.910 align:middle line:84%
And so then judging or
projecting onto the world that

00:03:00.910 --> 00:03:04.930 align:middle line:84%
is showing us the healing
process, the ability

00:03:04.930 --> 00:03:08.890 align:middle line:84%
to take sides and
maintain an external war,

00:03:08.890 --> 00:03:12.310 align:middle line:84%
that is really helping to
bring us into consciousness

00:03:12.310 --> 00:03:15.320 align:middle line:84%
with the inner
turmoil within us.

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:18.210 align:middle line:84%
And so when I teach
an open-hearted path,

00:03:18.210 --> 00:03:20.680 align:middle line:84%
it is simply because
the opening of the heart

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:23.480 align:middle line:84%
is what relaxes
the nervous system.

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:26.290 align:middle line:84%
When we talk about the
thinning of the veils and unity

00:03:26.290 --> 00:03:28.620 align:middle line:84%
consciousness awakening
in human beings,

00:03:28.620 --> 00:03:32.950 align:middle line:84%
it is actually the veil
