children, we're here

00:05:43.730 --> 00:05:46.100 align:middle line:84%
to hold these feelings
in our sacred heart.

00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:48.590 align:middle line:84%
We're here to let them
voice their opinion.

00:05:48.590 --> 00:05:50.690 align:middle line:84%
We're here to give them
the unconditional love,

00:05:50.690 --> 00:05:53.810 align:middle line:84%
and attention, and affection
