00:07:51.890 --> 00:07:52.890 align:middle line:90%
the greater good of all.

00:07:52.890 --> 00:07:54.477 align:middle line:84%
>> External empowered
decision-making?

00:07:54.477 --> 00:07:56.810 align:middle line:84%
>> Decision-making that affects
the greater good of all.

00:07:56.810 --> 00:07:59.120 align:middle line:84%
>> And will you explain--
break down external empowered

00:07:59.120 --> 00:07:59.780 align:middle line:90%
decision-making?

00:07:59.780 --> 00:07:59.990 align:middle line:90%
I like that.

00:07:59.990 --> 00:08:00.790 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:08:00.790 --> 00:08:04.460 align:middle line:84%
So sacred activism or as I just
said, it kind of came to me.

00:08:04.460 --> 00:08:08.480 align:middle line:84%
When we are in that
vibration of sacred activism,

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:11.762 align:middle line:84%
our external empowered
decision-making--

00:08:11.762 --> 00:08:13.220 align:middle line:84%
I love what I bring,
just something

00:08:13.220 --> 00:08:14.750 align:middle line:90%
brand new in the moment--

00:08:14.750 --> 00:08:17.600 align:middle line:84%
is actually
decisions and choices

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:20.210 align:middle line:84%
for what we're for
and not against.

00:08:20.210 --> 00:08:24.650 align:middle line:84%
When our decisions are trying
to take down what we're against,

00:08:24.650 --> 00:08:28.640 align:middle line:84%
that is actually a sign
that our inner activist

00:08:28.640 --> 00:08:30.980 align:middle line:84%
has become an
inner victim and is

00:08:30.980 --> 00:08:34.760 align:middle line:84%
a reminder that our nervous
system has got disrupted.

00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:36.320 align:middle line:90%
It is overstimulated.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:40.220 align:middle line:84%
And we are now trying to be an
activist from a state of fight

00:08:40.220 --> 00:08:41.330 align:middle line:90%
or flight.

00:08:41.330 --> 00:08:43.520 align:middle line:84%
That is like an inner
alarm clock that goes

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.800 align:middle line:84%
off emotionally
that says, I'm not

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:48.680 align:middle line:84%
going to perpetuate
external war.

00:08:48.680 --> 00:08:51.860 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to stop and give
time to my inner turmoil,

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:56.270 align:middle line:84%
because right now, I'm fighting
against something instead

00:08:56.270 --> 00:08:57.740 align:middle line:90%
of what I'm for.

00:08:57.740 --> 00:09:01.220 align:middle line:84%
So I take the time to be
with my own heart to tune

00:09:01.220 --> 00:09:04.550 align:middle line:84%
into my inner child, to
the innocence within me

00:09:04.550 --> 00:09:08.980 align:middle line:84%
that hurts as a reflection
of those that hurt me.

00:09:08.980 --> 00:09:11.300 align:middle line:84%
And how can I be
that for myself,

00:09:11.300 --> 00:09:14.180 align:middle line:84%
which my past
neglected to offer me?

00:09:14.180 --> 00:09:17.900 align:middle line:84%
I think a lot of times people
get so gung-ho on activism

00:09:17.900 --> 00:09:20.630 align:middle line:84%
that we don't stop
to decide, am I

00:09:20.630 --> 00:09:23.960 align:middle line:84%
making decisions
for what I'm for

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:26.720 align:middle line:90%
or fighting against something?

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:28.550 align:middle line:84%
And whenever we're
against something,

00:09:28.550 --> 00:09:32.570 align:middle line:84%
that is literally the evidence
that we need to pull ourselves

00:09:32.570 --> 00:09:34.130 align:middle line:90%
off of a battlefield.

00:09:34.130 --> 00:09:37.550 align:middle line:84%
We need to take time to
really love our own self

00:09:37.550 --> 00:09:39.980 align:middle line:84%
and not be so attached
to the outcomes we're

00:09:39.980 --> 00:09:42.290 align:middle line:84%
trying to promote,
that we disregard

00:09:42.290 --> 00:09:44.360 align:middle line:90%
our own internal healing.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:46.880 align:middle line:84%
Because sacred activism
is only a change

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:48.890 align:middle line:84%
that will be
brought to the world

00:09:48.890 --> 00:09:53.630 align:middle line:84%
by a collective force of
aligned heart-centered beings.

00:09:53.630 --> 00:09:56.090 align:middle line:84%
So we learn to know
when we're aligned

00:09:56.090 --> 00:09:57.560 align:middle line:90%
and when we're not aligned.

00:09:57.560 --> 00:10:00.530 align:middle line:84%
When we're against something,
we stop right then and there.

00:10:00.530 --> 00:10:03.290 align:middle line:84%
Because no amount of action
from a misaligned place

00:10:03.290 --> 00:10:06.530 align:middle line:84%
is going to do anything
but promote the very energy

00:10:06.530 --> 00:10:08.600 align:middle line:90%
that many people are against.

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:12.005 align:middle line:84%
And so then we switch sides, not
knowing it, with a wellness--

00:10:12.005 --> 00:10:14.220 align:middle line:84%
>> That's running our
movements or our actions.

00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:15.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:10:15.020 --> 00:10:16.970 align:middle line:84%
With a well-intended,
optimistic campaign,

00:10:16.970 --> 00:10:18.560 align:middle line:84%
we're actually
feeling the things.

00:10:18.560 --> 00:10:20.290 align:middle line:90%
We have more things to defeat.

00:10:20.290 --> 00:10:21.790 align:middle line:84%
So whenever we're
against something,

00:10:21.790 --> 00:10:23.230 align:middle line:90%
we stop what we're doing.

00:10:23.230 --> 00:10:25.630 align:middle line:90%
We make time to love ourselves.

