00:10:49.450 --> 00:10:52.840 align:middle line:84%
So when we are aligned
in sacred activism,

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:56.560 align:middle line:84%
our empowered external
decision-making is about,

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:58.810 align:middle line:90%
