the world how to treat us,

00:11:10.270 --> 00:11:11.830 align:middle line:90%
by how we treat others.

00:11:11.830 --> 00:11:14.290 align:middle line:84%
And the moment we
turn against anything,

00:11:14.290 --> 00:11:18.910 align:middle line:84%
